decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to overwhelm your opponent with fast and aggressive creatures and burn spells. By utilizing low-cost creatures like Monastery Swiftspear and Ghitu Lavarunner, as well as powerful burn spells such as Play with Fire and Wizard's Lightning, the deck aims to deal damage quickly and efficiently. Cards like Soul-Scar Mage and Kumano Faces Kakkazan provide additional versatility and synergy with the deck's overall strategy. The inclusion of Jegantha, the Wellspring as a companion allows for additional ramp and consistency in casting the deck's powerful spells.

This deck aims to overwhelm opponents with a quick and aggressive strategy utilizing artifact creatures and spells. By quickly buffing up artifacts with cards like Ensoul Artifact and Torch the Tower, as well as utilizing cards like Shrapnel Blast for direct damage, the deck can put pressure on opponents early on. Additionally, the inclusion of Jegantha, the Wellspring as a companion provides additional flexibility and power to the deck. Overall, the focus is on utilizing artifacts to quickly build a formidable board presence and win the game before opponents can react effectively.
